<lb n="0780b03" ed="T"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="001"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="001"/><cb:jhead><title><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780008" type="orig">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780008">佛說【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0780008"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>孝子經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0780b04" ed="T"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0780b05"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0780009" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">（（失譯…晉錄））＝失譯【宋】【元】，失譯人名【明】</note><note n="0780009" type="mod" resp="CBETA">失譯…晉錄【大】，失譯【宋】【元】，失譯人名【明】</note><app cb:word-count="9" n="0780009"><lem wit="【大】">失譯<note type="orig" n="0780010" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔人名〕－【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780010" resp="CBETA">人名【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0780010"><lem wit="【大】">人名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>今附西晉錄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">失譯</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">失譯人名</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0780b06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT16p0780b0601">佛問諸沙門：「親之生子，懷<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780011" type="orig">之＝抱【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780011" type="mod">之【大】，抱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780011"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">抱</rdg></app>十月，身為重
<lb ed="T" n="0780b07"/>病；臨生之日，母危父怖，其情難言。既生之
<lb n="0780b08" ed="T"/>後，推燥臥濕，精誠之至，血化為乳，摩<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780012">拭＝飾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780012" type="mod" resp="CBETA">拭【大】，飾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780012"><lem wit="【大】">拭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飾</rdg></app>澡
<lb n="0780b09" ed="T"/>浴，衣食教詔，禮賂師友，<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780013">奉＝重【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780013">奉【大】，重【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780013"><lem wit="【大】">奉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">重</rdg></app>貢君長；子顏和
<lb n="0780b10" ed="T"/>悅，親亦欣豫，子設慘<note n="0780014" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">慼＝戚【三】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780014" type="mod">慼【大】，戚【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0780014"><lem wit="【大】">慼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">戚</rdg></app>，親心焦枯；<note type="orig" n="0780015" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">（（出門…之））八字＝入門存之出顧履履【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780015" resp="CBETA">（出門…之）八字【大】，入門存之出顧履履【宮】</note><app n="0780015" cb:word-count="8"><lem wit="【大】">出門愛
<lb n="0780b11" ed="T"/>念，入則存之</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">入門存之出顧履履</rdg></app>，心懷惕惕，懼其不<note type="orig" n="0780016" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">善＝成【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780016" resp="CBETA">善【大】，成【宮】</note><app n="0780016"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app>。親恩若
<lb ed="T" n="0780b12"/><note type="orig" n="0780017" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">此＋（當）【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780017">此【大】，此當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780017"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">此當</rdg></app>，何以報<note n="0780018" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780018" resp="CBETA">之【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780018"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>？」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0780b1206" rend="inline">諸沙門對曰：「唯當盡禮慈心
<lb n="0780b13" ed="T"/>供養，以賽<note type="orig" n="0780019" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">親＝養【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780019" resp="CBETA">親【大】，養【宮】</note><app n="0780019"><lem wit="【大】">親</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">養</rdg></app><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780020" type="orig">恩＋（耳）【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780020" resp="CBETA">恩【大】，恩耳【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780020"><lem wit="【大】">恩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">恩耳</rdg></app>。」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0780b1307">世尊又曰：「子之養親，甘露
<lb n="0780b14" ed="T"/>百味以<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780021">恣＝咨【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780021">恣【大】，咨【宮】</note><app n="0780021"><lem wit="【大】">恣</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">咨</rdg></app>其口，天樂眾音以娛其耳，名衣
<lb n="0780b15" ed="T"/>上服光耀其<note n="0780022" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">身＝體【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780022" resp="CBETA">身【大】，體【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780022"><lem wit="【大】">身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">體</rdg></app>，兩肩荷負周流四海，訖子
<lb n="0780b16" ed="T"/>年命以賽<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780023" type="orig">養恩＝恩養【三】</note><note type="mod" n="0780023" resp="CBETA">養恩【大】，恩養【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0780023"><lem wit="【大】">養恩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">恩養</rdg></app>，可謂孝乎？」</p><p rend="inline" xml:id="pT16p0780b1611">諸沙門曰：「<note n="0780024" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">惟＝唯【宮】</note><note n="0780024" type="mod" resp="CBETA">惟【大】，唯【宮】</note><app n="0780024"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>
<lb n="0780b17" ed="T"/>孝之大莫尚<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780025" type="orig">乎＝干【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780025" type="mod">乎【大】，干【宮】</note><app n="0780025"><lem wit="【大】">乎</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">干</rdg></app>茲？」</p><p xml:id="pT16p0780b1708" rend="inline">世尊<note n="0780026" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔告〕－【宮】</note><note n="0780026" type="mod" resp="CBETA">告【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0780026"><lem wit="【大】">告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>曰：「未為孝矣！若
<lb n="0780b18" ed="T"/>親頑闇不奉三尊，兇虐殘戾，濫竊非<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780027" type="orig">理婬妷＝物情染【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780027">理婬妷【大】，物情染【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780027"><lem wit="【大】">理，婬
<lb ed="T" n="0780b19"/>妷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">物情染</rdg></app>外色，偽辭非道，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780028" type="orig">酖愐＝耽醉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780028" type="mod" resp="CBETA">酖愐【大】，耽醉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780028"><lem wit="【大】">酖愐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">耽醉</rdg></app>荒亂，違背正真，兇
<lb n="0780b20" ed="T"/>㜸若<note type="orig" n="0780029" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">斯＝此【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780029" resp="CBETA">斯【大】，此【宮】</note><app n="0780029"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">此</rdg></app>，子當極諫以啟悟之。<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780030" type="orig">〔若〕－【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780030" type="mod">若【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0780030"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>猶瞢瞢未
<lb n="0780b21" ed="T"/>悟，即為<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780031">義化當＝開化【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780031" resp="CBETA">義化當【大】，開化【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780031"><lem wit="【大】">義化，當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">開化</rdg></app>牽<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780032">譬＝<g ref="#CB13520"/>【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780032">譬【大】，<g ref="#CB13520"/>【宮】</note><app n="0780032"><lem wit="【大】">譬</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho"><g ref="#CB13520"/></rdg></app>引類，示王者之牢獄、
<lb ed="T" n="0780b22"/>諸囚之刑戮曰：『斯為不軌，身被眾毒，自招
<lb ed="T" n="0780b23"/>殞命。命終神去，繫于太山，湯火萬毒，獨<note n="0780033" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">呼＝喚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780033" type="mod" resp="CBETA">呼【大】，喚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780033"><lem wit="【大】">呼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">喚</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0780b24"/>無救。由彼履惡，遭<note n="0780034" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">斯＝此【三】【宮】＊</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780034">斯【大】＊，此【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0780034"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此</rdg></app>重殃<note n="0780035" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">矣設＝若【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780035" resp="CBETA">矣設【大】，若【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780035"><lem wit="【大】">矣。』設</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">若</rdg></app>復未移，
<lb n="0780b25" ed="T"/><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780036">吟＝悲【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780036" type="mod">吟【大】，悲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780036"><lem wit="【大】">吟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悲</rdg></app>泣啼<note n="0780037" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">嗷＝號【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780037" type="mod">嗷【大】，號【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780037"><lem wit="【大】">嗷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">號</rdg></app>，絕<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780038" type="orig">不＝無【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780038" type="mod">不【大】，無【宮】</note><app n="0780038"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">無</rdg></app>飲食，親雖不明，必以恩
<lb ed="T" n="0780b26"/>愛之痛，懼子死矣。<note type="orig" n="0780039" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">猶＝由【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780039">猶【大】，由【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780039"><lem wit="【大】">猶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">由</rdg></app>當強忍伏心崇<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780040">（正）＋道【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780040" type="mod" resp="CBETA">道【大】，正道【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780040"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">正道</rdg></app>，若
<lb ed="T" n="0780b27"/>親遷志奉佛五戒，仁<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780041">惻＝測【明】，懼【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780041" resp="CBETA">惻【大】，測【明】，懼【宮】</note><app n="0780041"><lem wit="【大】">惻</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">測</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">懼</rdg></app>不殺，清讓不盜，貞
<lb n="0780b28" ed="T"/>潔不婬，守信不欺，孝順不醉<note type="orig" n="0780042" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780042" type="mod" resp="CBETA">者【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780042"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，宗門之內，
<lb n="0780b29" ed="T"/>即<note n="0780043" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">親＋（父）【宮】</note><note n="0780043" type="mod" resp="CBETA">親【大】，親父【宮】</note><app n="0780043"><lem wit="【大】">親</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">親父</rdg></app>慈子孝，夫正婦貞，九族和睦，僕使<note n="0780044" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">順從＝恭順【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780044" type="mod">順從【大】，恭順【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780044"><lem wit="【大】">順
<pb ed="T" xml:id="T16.0687.0780c" n="0780c"/>
<lb n="0780c01" ed="T"/>從</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">恭順</rdg></app>，潤澤遠被，含血受恩，十方諸佛、天龍鬼神、
<lb n="0780c02" ed="T"/>有道之君、忠平之臣，黎庶萬姓無不敬愛，祐
<lb n="0780c03" ed="T"/>而安之。<note n="0780045" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">數＝雖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780045" type="mod" resp="CBETA">數【大】，雖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780045"><lem wit="【大】">數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雖</rdg></app>有顛倒之政，<g ref="#CB02439"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780046" type="orig">嬖＝<g ref="#CB00858"/>【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780046" type="mod">嬖【大】，<g ref="#CB00858"/>【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780046"><lem wit="【大】">嬖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><g ref="#CB00858"/></rdg></app>之輔，兇兒妖
<lb n="0780c04" ed="T"/>婦，千邪萬怪，無如已何。<note n="0780047" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">於＝如【宮】</note><note n="0780047" type="mod" resp="CBETA">於【大】，如【宮】</note><app n="0780047"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">如</rdg></app>是二親處世常
<lb n="0780c05" ed="T"/>安，壽終魂靈<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780048" type="orig">往＝昇【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780048" type="mod" resp="CBETA">往【大】，昇【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780048"><lem wit="【大】">往</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">昇</rdg></app>生天上，諸佛共會得聞法
<lb ed="T" n="0780c06"/>言，獲道度世長與苦別。」</p>
<lb ed="T" n="0780c07"/><p xml:id="pT16p0780c0701">佛告諸沙門：「覩世無孝，唯斯為孝耳。能令<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780049">（二）＋親【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780049">親【大】，二親【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780049"><lem wit="【大】">親</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">二親</rdg></app>
<lb ed="T" n="0780c08"/>去惡為善，奉持五戒，執三<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780050">自＝貞【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780050">自【大】，貞【宮】</note><app n="0780050"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">貞</rdg></app>歸，朝奉而暮
<lb ed="T" n="0780c09"/>終者，恩重於親乳哺之養、無量之惠。若不能
<lb ed="T" n="0780c10"/>以三尊之至化其親者，雖為<note n="0780051" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">孝＝前【宮】</note><note n="0780051" type="mod" resp="CBETA">孝【大】，前【宮】</note><app n="0780051"><lem wit="【大】">孝</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">前</rdg></app>養<note n="0780052" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">猶＝由【宮】</note><note n="0780052" type="mod" resp="CBETA">猶【大】，由【宮】</note><app n="0780052"><lem wit="【大】">猶</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">由</rdg></app><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780053">為不孝＝不孝矣【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780053">為不孝【大】，不孝矣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780053"><lem wit="【大】">為不
<lb n="0780c11" ed="T"/>孝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">不孝矣</rdg></app>。無以<g ref="#CB00858"/>妻遠賢不親，女情多欲，好色無倦，
<lb n="0780c12" ed="T"/>違孝<note type="orig" n="0780054" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">殺＝敬【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780054" resp="CBETA">殺【大】，敬【宮】</note><app n="0780054"><lem wit="【大】">殺</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">敬</rdg></app>親，國政荒亂，萬民流<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780055" type="orig">亡＝忘【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780055" type="mod">亡【大】，忘【宮】</note><app n="0780055"><lem wit="【大】">亡</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">忘</rdg></app>；本志惠
<lb n="0780c13" ed="T"/>施，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780056" type="orig">禮＝以【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780056">禮【大】，以【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780056"><lem wit="【大】">禮</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780057">式＝戒【元】【明】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780057">式【大】，戒【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780057"><lem wit="【大】">式</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">戒</rdg></app>自<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780058">撿＝檢【明】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780058">撿【大】，檢【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780058"><lem wit="【大】">撿</lem><rdg wit="【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">檢</rdg></app>，<note n="0780059" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">〔軟〕－【宮】</note><note n="0780059" type="mod" resp="CBETA">軟【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0780059"><lem wit="【大】">軟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>心<note n="0780c1301" resp="CBETA" type="add">崇【CB】【麗-CB】，祟【大】</note><app n="0780c1301"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">崇<note type="cf1">K20n0827_p1143b23</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">祟</rdg></app>仁，<note n="0780060" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">烝烝＝蒸蒸【三】，拯【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780060" resp="CBETA">烝烝【大】，蒸蒸【宋】【元】【明】，拯【宮】</note><app n="0780060"><lem wit="【大】">烝烝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">蒸蒸</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">拯</rdg></app>進德，潛
<lb ed="T" n="0780c14"/>意寂寞，學志叡達，名<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780061" type="orig">動＝勳【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780061" type="mod">動【大】，勳【宮】</note><app n="0780061"><lem wit="【大】">動</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">勳</rdg></app>諸天，明齊賢者，自
<lb n="0780c15" ed="T"/>穢妻聚，惑志女色，荒迷<note n="0780062" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">于＝子【宮】</note><note n="0780062" type="mod" resp="CBETA">于【大】，子【宮】</note><app n="0780062"><lem wit="【大】">于</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">子</rdg></app>欲，妖<note type="orig" n="0780063" place="foot text" resp="Taisho">蠱姿態＝治恣能【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780063" resp="CBETA">蠱姿態【大】，治恣能【宮】</note><app n="0780063"><lem wit="【大】">蠱姿態</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">治恣能</rdg></app>其
<lb n="0780c16" ed="T"/>變萬端。薄智之夫、淺見之士，覩其如此，不
<lb ed="T" n="0780c17"/><note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780064">覺＝學【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780064">覺【大】，學【宮】</note><app n="0780064"><lem wit="【大】">覺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">學</rdg></app>微漸，遂迴志沒身，從彼<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780065" type="orig">魃魅＝妖媚【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780065">魃魅【大】，妖媚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780065"><lem wit="【大】">魃魅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">妖媚</rdg></app>邪巧之<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780066">亂＝辭【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780066" resp="CBETA">亂【大】，辭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780066"><lem wit="【大】">亂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">辭</rdg></app>，
<lb ed="T" n="0780c18"/>或危親殺君，<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780067" type="orig">悋＝悟【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0780067" type="mod">悋【大】，悟【宮】</note><app n="0780067"><lem wit="【大】">悋</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">悟</rdg></app>色情蕩，忿<note n="0780068" type="orig" resp="Taisho" place="foot text">嫉＝戾【宮】</note><note n="0780068" type="mod" resp="CBETA">嫉【大】，戾【宮】</note><app n="0780068"><lem wit="【大】">嫉</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">戾</rdg></app>怠慢，散心盲
<lb ed="T" n="0780c19"/><note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0780069" type="orig">冥＝瞑【三】【宮】</note><note type="mod" n="0780069" resp="CBETA">冥【大】，瞑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780069"><lem wit="【大】">冥</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">瞑</rdg></app>，等行鳥獸，自古世來，無不由之<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0780070">殺＝亡【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0780070">殺【大】，亡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780070"><lem wit="【大】">殺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">亡</rdg></app>身滅
<pb ed="T" xml:id="T16.0687.0781a" n="0781a"/>
<lb ed="T" n="0781a01"/>宗。是以沙門獨而不雙，清潔其志<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0781001">以＝唯【三】【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" type="mod" n="0781001">以【大】，唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781001"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>道是
<lb n="0781a02" ed="T"/>務。奉<app type="star" corresp="#0780034"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此</rdg></app>明<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0781002" type="orig">戒＝教【宮】</note><note resp="CBETA" n="0781002" type="mod">戒【大】，教【宮】</note><app n="0781002"><lem wit="【大】">戒</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">教</rdg></app>，為君即保四海，為臣即忠，
<lb n="0781a03" ed="T"/>以仁養民，<note place="foot text" resp="Taisho" type="orig" n="0781003">〔即〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781003" type="mod" resp="CBETA">即【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781003"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>父法明子孝慈，夫信婦貞。優
<lb ed="T" n="0781a04"/>婆塞、優婆夷執行如<note resp="Taisho" place="foot text" n="0781004" type="orig">是＝此【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781004" type="mod" resp="CBETA">是【大】，此【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781004"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">此</rdg></app>，世世逢佛見法得道。」</p>
<lb n="0781a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT16p0781a0501">佛說如是，弟子歡喜。</p></cb:div>
